00:37:48,690 --> 00:37:50,619
You did? You big hero!

487
00:37:51,090 --> 00:37:54,570
No. I was reckless.
I put everyone in grave peril.

488
00:37:58,889 --> 00:38:00,610
Angel is the true champion.

489
00:38:03,090 --> 00:38:04,949
- He saved us.
- Did you hear that?

490
00:38:06,090 --> 00:38:07,210
Yeah, but--

491
00:38:07,889 --> 00:38:11,150
How many guys would
give away the credit like that?

492
00:38:13,289 --> 00:38:15,360
That is just so noble. The potion.

493
00:38:18,090 --> 00:38:19,489
Let's get out of here.

494
00:38:19,889 --> 00:38:21,010
See you.

495
00:38:22,889 --> 00:38:24,079
Cordelia.

496
00:38:24,090 --> 00:38:25,170
What?

497
00:38:34,889 --> 00:38:36,219
What is it?

498
00:38:42,090 --> 00:38:44,510
- What's this?
- Just some money I saved up.

499
00:38:45,090 --> 00:38:46,170
Why? What for?

500
00:38:47,489 --> 00:38:51,000
I did something for you tonight. Now
I want you to do something for me.

501
00:38:54,090 --> 00:38:57,500
Don't come in tomorrow.
Don't come in for a couple of weeks.

502
00:38:58,889 --> 00:39:03,489
Take Groo someplace nice.
Someplace where there's sun.

503
00:39:05,489 --> 00:39:06,820
You'd like that.

504
00:39:08,489 --> 00:39:10,809
- Angel--
- Promise me.

505
00:39:14,489 --> 00:39:15,650
Okay.

506
00:39:23,489 --> 00:39:25,809
You sure you don't need
some patching up?

507
00:39:27,690 --> 00:39:29,829
I'm good. Didn't hurt a bit.

508
00:39:56,489 --> 00:39:59,750
All right, now.
You get some rest, big boy.

509
00:40:00,090 --> 00:40:04,619
Yes. You go to sleep.
Get you nice and tucked in.

510
00:40:06,090 --> 00:40:07,250
Yes.

511
00:40:09,090 --> 00:40:13,480
- Thanks for looking after him.
- Yeah, sure. You okay?

512
00:40:17,489 --> 00:40:18,650
Yeah.

513
00:40:50,489 --> 00:40:52,769
- Working late?
- Yes.

514
00:40:54,690 --> 00:40:57,110
- You startled me.
- Oh, we didn't mean to.

515
00:40:58,889 --> 00:41:02,440
- I thought I was alone.
- Yeah. So did I.